   Robustness finding:&nbsp;CS &gt; 0 across all parameter combinations tested. Even under the most conservative assumptions (high discount rate, high S_max, low SCC, short externality tail), the McDowell County IPG &ge; 5&times; &mdash; the market price covers at most 20% of the true cost. The central finding is robust to parameter uncertainty; only the magnitude varies.
